e64ad800a0b2d9effb478e45b","msg_type":"text","content":"让他部署","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:24:01+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"chat_id":"oc_40bbff03960c833503d8cd0f8a490d26","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e5a3f0f8acc3037d767be9fa1","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card title=\"🦐  50秒一键领取你的专属龙虾，无需任何配置！\">\n<clickable url=\"https://miaoda.feishu.cn/bot?open-from=claw_live\">\n🖼️ 图片\n</clickable>\n**🚀  获取你的专属龙虾**\n**方式一：50秒一键领养！**👉[点击一键养“虾”](https://miaoda.feishu.cn/bot?open-from=claw_live)\n适合0基础小白\n**方式二：已经有虾老出问题？史上最详细龙虾康复攻略**👇👇👇\n👉 [查看完整部署教程](https://larkcommunity.feishu.cn/wiki/LDmXwEVhJitBa5kU0mjc16VKneb)\n\n---\n**🚀 龙虾可以干啥？**\n📄**自动创建文档**\n**基于评论修改并生成新文档 **\n\n💬**总结群聊内容**\n**整理待办任务 **\n📉**自动创建多维表格**\n**批量导入数据 **\n\n💡**总结今日会议**\n**明确跟进事项 **\n**👉 **[点击前往获取提示词](https://bytedance.larkoffice.com/wiki/Vbk9w0oIMiFFJekDGENcZOPLnwe)\n---\n**🦞 快来部署你的第一个“龙虾”助理，玩转“龙虾”！玩转飞书！**\n\n更多攻略：👉 [妙搭养“虾”攻略](https://bytedance.larkoffice.com/wiki/S8InwrisCieEBtkm6zBcbZWQnrg)\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a018f84884b8500c","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:17:55+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"chat_id":"oc_faa7202e9c9a201a246d8fcfd4a22bf1"},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e5bb35e0b0c34237e3018bef0","msg_type":"post","content":"我看到这个群（oc_58f857cae2301a603c511bc8279bf35f）里目前有一个机器人：\n- **金融虾** (cli_a93109b4a1791bca) - 帮你做金融分析的\n你说的是让\"金融虾\"去部署 paperclipai/paperclip 项目吗？还是\"技术虾\"是另外一个机器人？\n如果是让金融虾去部署，我可以在群里发一条消息让它开始部署。你确认一下我就帮你发。","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:20:15+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e5bae79cb0b22459b66fb491e","chat_id":"oc_40bbff03960c833503d8cd0f8a490d26","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e5b505c4a0b391a5a457d6f2d","msg_type":"text","content":"部署一下这个 GitHub 项目：https://github.com/paperclipai/paperclip","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:21:48+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"chat_id":"oc_eb1229e94d574cb07b59857f8d86c89a","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_3199a2d84d6a711868a6ecf1ded3ba32"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e7998ffcb4b49596e76b991e0","msg_type":"post","content":"**第8轮 · 尚书省**：\n中书省所引\"敏捷开发\"，实为深思熟虑后的快速迭代，岂是不做预判的盲动？华为今日之技术突破，正是十余年\"信息前置\"——提前布局芯片、操作系统——的远见所致，岂是仓促应战可得？至于空城计，诸葛亮唱得此计，靠的是先前对司马懿性格与兵力部署的精密研判；若未事先掌握敌方情报，空城便是真正的坟墓。真正的怯懦，是在信息洪流中放弃判断力，以\"敏捷\"为名行鲁莽之实，把国家和人民的命运押在侥幸之上。","sender":{"id":"cli_a9379ce69ca25bcd","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T20:28:36+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"chat_id":"oc_a9dfdee2cec20f790c93bfdb8a95c355","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_97269b966ae7aee388bf97bc7f6196e2"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e51f9afc88b3fa37d5f3d75dd","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\n可以部署到本地。基础步骤如下：\n\n**1. 环境准备**\n\n```bash\n# 克隆项目\ngit clone https://github.com/TauricResearch/TradingAgents.git\ncd TradingAgents\n\n# 创建 Python 3.13 环境（需要 conda 或 pyenv）\nconda create -n tradingagents python=3.13\nconda activate tradingagents\n\n# 安装依赖\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n\n**2. 配置 API 密钥**\n根据你想使用的模型，设置对应的环境变量：\n\n```bash\n# OpenAI (GPT)\nexport OPENAI_API_KEY=\"sk-...\"\n\n# Anthropic (Claude)\nexport ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=\"sk-ant-...\"\n\n# Google (Gemini)\nexport GOOGLE_API_KEY=\"AIza...\"\n\n# xAI (Grok)\nexport XAI_API_KEY=\"xai-...\"\n```\n\n\n**3. 运行示例**\n\n```python\nfrom TradingAgents import TradingAgent\n\nagent = TradingAgent(\n    tickers=[\"NVDA\", \"AAPL\"],\n    llm_provider=\"openai\"  # 或 anthropic/google/xai\n)\nagent.run()\n```\n\n\n**需要确认几点：**\n1. 你本地有 Python 3.13 环境吗？还是需要我帮你用 Docker 部署？\n2. 想用哪个 LLM 提供商？（需要你自行准备 API Key）要我帮你直接在本地部署测试一下吗？\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a93109b4a1791bca","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T17:36:21+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e51eaa04a8b10e62fab96239a","chat_id":"oc_58f857cae2301a603c511bc8279bf35f","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_0f0cf151c57047db0d701cecd1ca9bec"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e6bf8134acb4b80925d754ab5","msg_type":"text","content":"[zhaoxinyi02/ClawPanel: 🐾 ClawPanel — OpenClaw AI 助手可视化管理面板。Go 单二进制部署，支持 20+ 通道统一管理，跨平台，实时日志监控。](https://github.com/zhaoxinyi02/ClawPanel)","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T19:27:16+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"chat_id":"oc_eb1229e94d574cb07b59857f8d86c89a","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_3199a2d84d6a711868a6ecf1ded3ba32"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e6cd5580b0b34f6aacfdb97c5","msg_type":"post","content":"🎉 **Paperclip 部署成功！**\n已创建：\n- **公司**：赚钱公司\n- **Agent**：CEO\n- **任务**：Create your CEO [HEARTBEAT.md](HEARTBEAT.md)\n有一个问题：Agent 运行失败，提示 \"claude\" command not found。这是因为本地没有安装 Claude Code。\n你需要安装 [Claude Code](https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/intro) 才能让 Agent 工作。\n安装后告诉我，我再帮你测试。","sender":{"id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:58:01+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e6335064a8b103440cf49214f","chat_id":"oc_eb1229e94d574cb07b59857f8d86c89a","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_3199a2d84d6a711868a6ecf1ded3ba32"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e72f7310a4b2965a2156bbf2d","msg_type":"post","content":"🎉 **ClawPanel 部署成功！**\n**访问地址**：[http://127.0.0.1:19527](http://127.0.0.1:19527)\n**密码**：wanghanghao123\n你现在可以看到：\n- ✅ OpenClaw 运行中\n- ✅ 飞书通道已启用\n- ✅ 网关在线\n- ✅ 系统运行正常","sender":{"id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T19:57:16+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e71bbf28a4b393a0d791ee84a","chat_id":"oc_eb1229e94d574cb07b59857f8d86c89a","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_3199a2d84d6a711868a6ecf1ded3ba32"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e5a0c3d080b3b576468960869","msg_type":"post","content":"我目前没有找到关于\"技术虾\"的信息。你能告诉我\"技术虾\"是谁吗？\n- 是某个特定的用户/助手？\n- 是某个机器人账号？\n- 还是其他联系方式？\n告诉我后，我可以帮你通知他去部署。","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:18:09+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e5a5136ca4b3309b598acaf37","chat_id":"oc_40bbff03960c833503d8cd0f8a490d26","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e5b77e08e8b21b168f1bafdb1","msg_type":"post","content":"需要在群里先授权才能发消息。你在群里点击授权链接完成授权后，告诉我一声，我再帮你发部署指令。","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:21:15+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e5b68008b4b4b00b36824ee22","chat_id":"oc_40bbff03960c833503d8cd0f8a490d26","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e5bc0664b4c3ec368d00da3e9","msg_type":"post","content":"抱歉，我在飞书联系人中没有找到\"技术虾\"这个机器人账号。\n可能的原因：\n1. 该机器人不在我的联系人列表中\n2. 机器人名称可能有差异\n你能提供以下信息吗：\n- 机器人的准确名称\n- 或者机器人所在的群聊名称\n- 或者机器人的 open_id（如果有的话）\n这样我可以帮你联系它去部署。","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:19:24+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e5bfaae4b4b2d48a92ee1c6ba","chat_id":"oc_40bbff03960c833503d8cd0f8a490d26","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e5b2c9e878b3fad404c1928a1","msg_type":"post","content":"已发送！消息发到那个群里了，技术人会帮你部署 paperclipai/paperclip 项目。🦐","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T18:21:52+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e5b68008b4b4b00b36824ee22","chat_id":"oc_40bbff03960c833503d8cd0f8a490d26","chat_type":"p2p","chat_partner":{"open_id":"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d"}},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e5a5136ca4b3309b598acaf37","msg