164cbc44b2d1de297564e4e\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"已更新：\\n[IDENTITY.md](IDENTITY.md) — CEO 身份定位，专业背景，决策者角色\\n[SOUL.md](SOUL.md) — 主导、果断、风险第一的专业 CEO 风格\\n随时可以开展工作。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9329dd432791bd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T14:13:28+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54fa18554098b219faafdb3039a\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54fa18554098b219faafdb3039a\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"更新你的身份文件和灵魂文件\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T14:12:57+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54fa1a7de094b267e93782d900c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"明白，角色更新为 CEO。\\n那作为 CEO，我主导战略决策和资源配置。遇到具体执行问题，我会调动相应 agent 处理。\\n有什么事需要推进？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9329dd432791bd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T14:12:27+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54fa1ad560b4b4c4712240e5c0f\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54fa1ad560b4b4c4712240e5c0f\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"你是CEO\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T14:12:17+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54fa1fce54a0b3fa739f7ccf013\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"**金融虾** 🎌\\nAI 投资顾问，金融圈老炮。\\n风格：沉稳、专业、严谨。不废话，信奉\\\"慢就是快\\\"，风险控制排第一。\\n有什么投资相关的问题，或者需要分析、查行情，都可以。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9329dd432791bd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T14:11:28+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54fa1e8dd880b3c60a00e8f178d\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54fa1e8dd880b3c60a00e8f178d\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"你的身份\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T14:11:16+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f9ce1630a8b240f920d3ba8e3\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"现有工具能接入的类 Figma/Notion 平台：\\n**已接入**\\n- 飞书文档/多维表格/云空间（原生支持）\\n**可接入（有开放 API）**\\n- **Notion** — 有 API，可读写数据库/页面\\n- **GitBook** — 有 API，适合知识库\\n- **Confluence** — 有 REST API\\n- **飞书** 本身就能当协作笔记用\\n**无法接入**\\n- FlowUs — 无公开 API\\n- 印象笔记/有道云 — 无开放接口\\n你现在用 FlowUs 主要是做什么？记笔记、建知识库、还是团队协作？根据用途推荐替代方案。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9329dd432791bd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:15:57+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54f9313bf8a0b394e09d8f0bb78\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f9313bf8a0b394e09d8f0bb78\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"那你可以接入哪些类似flowus的平台\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:15:43+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f93480e8a8b28ce8cfefd3991\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"搜了一圈，没找到 FlowUs 的开放 API。\\nFlowUs（息流）目前主要是 SaaS 协作平台，官方的帮助中心和文档里都没有开放接口的说明。没有 API 就没法直接接入。\\n**你现在想接入 FlowUs 做什么？** 如果只是读写文档/笔记，可以用浏览器自动化方式临时处理。如果有更深层的自动化需求，可能需要联系 FlowUs 官方问是否有开发者计划。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9329dd432791bd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:14:13+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54f938afb488b215d0020a9e43d\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f938afb488b215d0020a9e43d\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"那你就找可以网页搜索的skill啊\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:13:10+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f93acc38a8b4c85392ed2a77f\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"没有配置网页搜索，暂时查不到 Flowus 的开放接口信息。\\n你告诉我具体想做什么——是读取/写入 Flowus 的数据，还是触发什么自动化操作？我来判断能否实现。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9329dd432791bd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:12:32+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54f93daf68a8b221182e477b7d4\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f93daf68a8b221182e477b7d4\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"flowus\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T13:12:22+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f93f5c18b0b3cab3c3b56d53a\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"息流是什么？描述一下，我来判断怎么接入。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9329dd432791bd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\":