单二进制部署，支持 20+ 通道统一管理，跨平台，实时日志监控。](https://github.com/zhaoxinyi02/ClawPanel)\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:27:16+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6a0e698a8b28cd4862de5868\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"已完全移除 Paperclip 项目！包括：\\n- ✅ 服务器已停止\\n- ✅ 项目文件已删除 (C:\\\\paperclip)\\n- ✅ 配置数据已删除 (C:\\\\Users\\\\Administrator\\\\.paperclip)\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:26:26+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e6a45558a4b35d9ab00f51099\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6a45558a4b35d9ab00f51099\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"整个项目都移除\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:25:29+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6a7ea74a4b39f58ae0aff291\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"已归档！现在页面显示的是另一个公司\\\"赚钱\\\"，之前的\\\"赚钱公司\\\"（CEO Agent）已经移除了。\\nPaperclip 服务器还在运行：[http://127.0.0.1:3100](http://127.0.0.1:3100)\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:25:06+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e69390a090b3dc9aa67768825\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e69390a090b3dc9aa67768825\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"算了不配置这个 用不了 直接移除吧\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:21:57+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e69dcfa4a4b3cf3bf154764ae\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"不一定！Paperclip 支持多种 Agent：\\n- **Claude Code** (需要登录/ API Key)\\n- **Codex** (本地)\\n- **OpenAI** (API Key)\\n- **Azure OpenAI**\\n- **Gemini**\\n你可以换个适配器。在 Paperclip 页面：\\n1. 进入 Agent 设置\\n2. 把 Adapter 改成 **OpenAI** 或其他支持的\\n或者你想用哪个？我帮你配置。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:19:12+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e69c4114a4b104bee7a8c4648\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e69c4114a4b104bee7a8c4648\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"一定要用这个吗\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:19:04+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e685dcaca4b37ed2fee3acb7c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"是的，Anthropic 在中国不可用。你可以：\\n1. **使用代理/VPN** 登录\\n2. **直接设置 API Key**（如果你有海外 API Key）\\n你有 API Key 吗？如果有告诉我，我直接帮你配置好。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:17:05+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e68478d880b3706bd20ecd26d\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e68478d880b3706bd20ecd26d\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"他好像不支持中国\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:16:59+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6883e70acb22bf21dfbf6000\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"我已打开了一个命令行窗口，运行 claude login。\\n你需要在那个窗口里：\\n1. 按提示输入你的 Anthropic 账号登录\\n2. 或者按 Ctrl+C 退出，然后告诉我你的 API Key，我直接帮你配置\\n那个命令行窗口应该在你屏幕上弹出了。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:15:59+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e688d08ca0b24d9151018a889\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e688d08ca0b24d9151018a889\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"哪里登录\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:15:45+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e68ae518a4b294fae1b46b758\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"需要设置 Claude Code 登录。你有两个选择：\\n1. **命令行登录**：运行 claude login 然后按提示操作\\n2. **设置 API Key**：告诉我你的 Anthropic API Key，我帮你配置\\n你有 API Key 吗？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:15:14+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e6f43e48a4b341e9af593fb54\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6f43e48a4b341e9af593fb54\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"你的首席执行官失败了\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:12:47+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6fc3658b0b31ab7d9e95cdc6\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Paperclip 已重启！现在 Claude Code 已在 PATH 中，你可以刷新浏览器页面测试 Agent，或者重新运行之前的任务试试。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:10:39+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e6e42cb8a4b318a49280d1e7c\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6e42cb8a4b318a49280d1e7c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"你不能直接安装吗\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T19:08:30+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6cd5580b0b34f6aacfdb97c5\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"🎉 **Paperclip 部署成功！**\\n已创建：\\n- **公司**：赚钱公司\\n- **Agent**：CEO\\n- **任务**：Create your CEO [HEARTBEAT.md](HEARTBEAT.md)\\n有一个问题：Agent 运行失败，提示 \\\"claude\\\" command not found。这是因为本地没有安装 Claude Code。\\n你需要安装 [Claude Code](https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/intro) 才能让 Agent 工作。\\n安装后告诉我，我再帮你测试。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T18:58:01+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e6335064a8b103440cf49214f\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e6335064a8b103440cf49214f\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"你自己打开检查下啊\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T18:56:26+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e622f4d8a0b382f6e64177fa1\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"从日志看，公司创建成功了（POST 返回 201），但页面变空白了。这可能是前端 JavaScript 错误。\\n请尝试：\\n1. 按 **F12** 打开浏览器开发者工具\\n2. 查看 **Console**（控制台）有没有红色错误信息\\n或者直接访问主页试试：[http://127.0.0.1:3100](http://127.0.0.1:3100)\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T18:51:47+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b54e611042100b213c036d67532d\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e611042100b213c036d67532d\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"赚钱\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T18:48:28+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    }\n  ],\n  \"has_more\": true,\n  \"page_token\": \"4cXSlmN7uFAnWWU5yfIGMIBXpY09pYmERjAtwQw6ZzU6_j1ABxGv5Gp4tLsQyS0RwZH6kI5YC_dT7LpvvgfKWVzwZtYZ9D5kVn_7GHdP6ZJ4Tu-zvzQaSmjGUu7IIhER\"\n}"}],"details":{"messages":[{"message_id":"om_x100b54e72f7310a4b2965a2156bbf2d","msg_type":"post","content":"🎉 **ClawPanel 部署成功！**\n**访问地址**：[http://127.0.0.1:19527](http://127.0.0.1:19527)\n**密码**：wanghanghao123\n你现在可以看到：\n- ✅ OpenClaw 运行中\n- ✅ 飞书通道已启用\n- ✅ 网关在线\n- ✅ 系统运行正常","sender":{"id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T19:57:16+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54e71bbf28a4b393a0d791ee84a"},{"message_id":"om_x100b54e71bbf28a4b393a0d791ee84a","msg_type":"text","content":"wanghanghao123","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T19:53:59+08:00","del