reate_time":"2026-03-20T00:15:20+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f641e1f8a4b36956e894aa8aa","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\n✅ 技能已全部复制到各 agent workspace，完成了，不需要做任何 git 操作。\n\n| Agent | 技能数 |\n|------|------|\n| coder | 10个智能增强技能 ✅ |\n| newsai | 10个智能增强技能 ✅ |\n| pm | 10个智能增强技能 ✅ |\n| finance | 10个智能增强技能 ✅ |\n|  |  |各 agent 之后启动时会自动加载这些技能。\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a9329dd432791bd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:14:43+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54f64068c0a4b2233ed2d12fa1e"},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f64068c0a4b2233ed2d12fa1e","msg_type":"text","content":"先安装skill不推送","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:14:34+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f644cd68acb378d286e474798","msg_type":"post","content":"每个 agent 的 workspace 都是独立 Git 仓库，没有配远程仓库。需要给每个建 GitHub repo 再推送。\n这个需要 GitHub 操作权限，我没有办法自动创建 GitHub repo。需要董事长在 GitHub 上手动创建 4 个空仓库：\n- openclaw-agent-coder\n- openclaw-agent-newsai\n- openclaw-agent-pm\n- `openclaw-agent-finance\n创建好后把对应的 SSH/HTTP URL 发给我，我来配置并推送。或者我先把各 agent 的变更提交到本地，等方便时再处理远程推送？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9329dd432791bd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:13:20+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54f648e82ca8b3fb77a9316169d"},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f648e82ca8b3fb77a9316169d","msg_type":"text","content":"把智能增强的给其他agnet也都安装上","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:12:18+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f5bb35d0acb340577c62e13f7","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\n已安装的智能增强类技能：\n\n| 技能 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| deep-thinking | 复杂问题深度推理框架 |\n| ai-researcher | 系统性深度研究与分析 |\n| adaptive-reasoning | 自动评估问题复杂度，动态调整推理深度 |\n| memory-manager | 本地记忆管理 + 自动快照 + 语义搜索 |\n| context-budgeting | 上下文窗口优化，防压缩丢失 |\n| automation-workflows | 工作流自动化设计 |\n| super-websearch-realtime | 实时网络搜索补充 |\n|  |  |核心三件套（已装在 workspace 根目录的全局技能）：\n\n| 技能 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| self-improving | 自我复盘与执行质量提升 |\n| proactivity | 主动预测与跟进 |\n| miliger-context-manager | 无缝会话切换 |\n|  |  |以上这些是真正能让我\"更聪明\"的部分。\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a9329dd432791bd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:07:59+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54f5bbf8b0a4c147a792d837709"},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f5bbf8b0a4c147a792d837709","msg_type":"text","content":"把能变聪明的skill列出来 已经安装的","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:07:47+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f5be56a4a4b389ba31c06999b","msg_type":"post","content":"金融虾遇到了 403 访问限制，没拿到数据。\n关于新技能的问题——是的，只装在主 workspace，其他 agent 各自独立。要现在把 deep-thinking、ai-researcher 等同步到 finance/coder/pm/newsai 的 workspace 吗？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9329dd432791bd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:06:33+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f5a15f60a8b21027a6f324ecf","msg_type":"post","content":"不是的。新装的技能只装在了**主 workspace**（~\\workspace\\skills\\），其他独立 agent（coder、pm、finance、newsai）有各自的独立 workspace，暂时还没有这些技能。\n如果想让每个 agent 都能用，需要分别往各自的 workspace 里也装一份。要我现在把新技能同步到各 agent 的 workspace 吗？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9329dd432791bd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:06:17+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54f5a0eb6ca0c4eb2e554a79fb8"},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f5a0eb6ca0c4eb2e554a79fb8","msg_type":"text","content":"新装的技能每个agent都有吗","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-20T00:05:54+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f5a6bab938b2da5ca7205cff3","msg_type":"post","content":"金融虾已唤醒，正在研究巴菲特投资哲学，稍等结果过来。","sender":{"id":"cli_a9329dd432791bd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-20