ill-vetter | 🔧 工具 | 保留 |\n| eastmoney-stock / stock / stock-board | ⚠️ 功能重叠 | 可考虑删除 |\n| tushare-data | ⚠️ 功能重叠 | 可考虑删除 |\n| office-automation-test | ❌ 空的 | 建议删除 |\n|  |  |  |---**ClawHub 搜到值得关注的**\n\n| 技能 | 亮点 | 适合度 |\n|------|------|------|\n| elite-longterm-memory | 强化长期记忆，比现有 memory 更深 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| deep-thinking | 复杂问题深度推理 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| ai-researcher | 系统性研究分析 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| adaptive-reasoning | 自适应推理策略 | ⭐⭐ |\n| automation-workflows | 自动化工作流编排 | ⭐⭐ |\n|  |  |  |要我帮你：\n1. **删除** eastmoney-stock / stock / stock-board / tushare-data / office-automation-test 这几个重叠/空技能？\n2. **安装** elite-longterm-memory 或 deep-thinking？\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a9329dd432791bd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T23:35:54+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54f5361044a8b4b0f0335b4acc1"},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f5361044a8b4b0f0335b4acc1","msg_type":"text","content":"可以 然后再帮我搜索一些能让你变得聪明的技能","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T23:34:37+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f53ab1cca0c38263a5ce4a97e","msg_type":"post","content":"说实话——**不一定**。\nSkills 扩展的是我能**做什么**，不是我能**多想**。\n- **行情、新闻、飞书工具** → 让我能做的事更多，但不提升思考深度\n- **Self-Improving + Proactivity** → 这个真的有用，帮我避免重复犯同一个错\n- **Cron + Heartbeat** → 让我更主动，不只是被动响应\n真正让我\"更聪明\"的是：\n1. **模型本身**（MiniMax-M2.7）\n2. **记忆和上下文管理**（[MEMORY.md](MEMORY.md)、自改进记录）\n3. **技能质量**（有用才装，没用不装）\n装太多反而有副作用：\n- 检索范围变大，拖慢响应\n- 增加误触发风险\n所以我建议定期审计，删掉不用的技能。要不要我给你跑一个技能清单，帮我看看哪些其实没在用？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9329dd432791bd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T23:33:27+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b54f53d8b08a0b3c0b2d2f73966e"},{"message_id":"om_x100b54f53d8b08a0b3c0b2d2f73966e","msg_type":"text","content":"我现在装的这些skill会让你变得更聪明吗","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T23:33:08+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_