{"type":"message","id":"1dec7028","parentId":"bf2cfb28","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:46:04.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a simple visualization page for viewing the memory records. Let me create a simple HTML page that can display the memory data.\n\nI'll create a simple web page that:\n1. Shows the memory stats\n2. Lists all memories\n3. Maybe allows searching/filtering\n\nLet me create this as an HTML file that can be served or opened directly.","thinkingSignature":"905a1389660280f5b112fdcb54ad7991ce8c58322ba803bba0c2249512121f92"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7pwuvs4k61vm_1","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/Administrator/.openclaw/workspace/memory-viewer.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Memory Viewer - OpenClaw</title>\n    <style>\n        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n        body { \n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            background: #1a1a2e; \n            color: #eee;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }\n        h1 { color: #00d9ff; margin-bottom: 20px; }\n        .stats { \n            display: grid; \n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n            gap: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .stat-card {\n            background: #16213e;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #0f3460;\n        }\n        .stat-card .label { color: #888; font-size: 14px; }\n        .stat-card .value { color: #00d9ff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; }\n        .memories { background: #16213e; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; }\n        .memories h2 { color: #00d9ff; margin-bottom: 15px; }\n        .memory-item {\n            background: #0f3460;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border-left: 4px solid #00d9ff;\n        }\n        .memory-item.preference { border-left-color: #f39c12; }\n        .memory-item.decision { border-left-color: #27ae60; }\n        .memory-item.fact { border-left-color: #9b59b6; }\n        .memory-meta { \n            font-size: 12px; \n            color: #888; \n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n        .memory-content { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; }\n        .memory-category {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #00d9ff;\n            color: #000;\n            padding: 2px 8px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 11px;\n            margin-left: 10px;\n        }\n        .refresh-btn {\n            background: #00d9ff;\n            color: #000;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border-radius: 6px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .refresh-btn:hover { background: #00b8d9; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>🧠 Memory Viewer - OpenClaw</h1>\n        <button class=\"refresh-btn\" onclick=\"loadMemories()\">🔄 刷新</button>\n        \n        <div class=\"stats\">\n            <div class=\"stat-card\">\n                <div class=\"label\">总记忆数</div>\n                <div class=\"value\" id=\"totalMemories\">-</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\">\n                <div class=\"label\">Scope 数量</div>\n                <div class=\"value\" id=\"scopeCount\">-</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\">\n                <div class=\"label\">检索模式</div>\n                <div class=\"value\" id=\"retrievalMode\">-</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-card\">\n                <div class=\"label\">Embedding 模型</div>\n                <div class=\"value\" id=\"embeddingModel\">-</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"memories\">\n            <h2>📝 记忆列表</h2>\n            <div id=\"memoryList\">加载中...</div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        async function loadMemories() {\n            const listEl = document.getElementById('memoryList');\n            listEl.innerHTML = '加载中...';\n            \n            try {\n                // Fetch stats\n                const statsRes = await fetch('http://127.0.0.1:18789/api/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/stats');\n                const stats = await statsRes.json();\n                \n                document.getElementById('totalMemories').textContent = stats.totalMemories || 0;\n                document.getElementById('scopeCount').textContent = stats.availableScopes?.length || 0;\n                document.getElementById('retrievalMode').textContent = stats.retrievalMode || 'N/A';\n                document.getElementById('embeddingModel').textContent = stats.embeddingModel || 'N/A';\n                \n                // Fetch memories\n                const listRes = await fetch('http://127.0.0.1:18789/api/plugins/memory-lancedb-pro/list');\n                const data = await listRes.json();\n                \n                const memories = data.memories || [];\n                \n                if (memories.length === 0) {\n                    listEl.innerHTML = '<p style=\"color:#888\">暂无记忆</p>';\n                    return;\n                }\n                \n                listEl.innerHTML = memories.map(m => `\n                    <div class=\"memory-item ${m.category || ''}\">\n                        <div class=\"memory-meta\">\n                            ${formatDate(m.createdAt)} \n                            <span class=\"memory-category\">${m.scope || 'default'}</span>\n                            ${m.category ? `<span class=\"memory-category\" style=\"background:${getCategoryColor(m.category)}\">${m.category}</span>` : ''}\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"memory-content\">${escapeHtml(m.content || m.text || '')}</div>\n                    </div>\n                `).join('');\n                \n            } catch (e) {\n                listEl.innerHTML = `<p style=\"color:#ff6b6b\">加载失败: ${e.message}</p>`;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        function formatDate(ts) {\n            if (!ts) return '';\n            const d = new Date(ts);\n            return d.toLocaleString('zh-CN');\n        }\n        \n        function escapeHtml(text) {\n            const div = document.createElement('div');\n            div.textContent = text;\n            return div.innerHTML;\n        }\n        \n        function getCategoryColor(cat) {\n            const colors = {\n                preference: '#f39c12',\n                decision: '#27ae60',\n                fact: '#9b59b6',\n                entity: '#3498db'\n            };\n            return colors[cat] || '#00d9ff';\n        }\n        \n        loadMemories();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":164,"output":1652,"cacheRead":153373,"cacheWrite":324,"totalTokens":155513,"cost":{"input":0.000049199999999999997,"output":0.0019824,"cacheRead":0.00460119,"cacheWrite":0.000038879999999999994,"total":0.006671669999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774075536874}}
